divs: Sighting DetailsWe observed 3 bright lights in unison flying low in the sky. It appeared triangular as if the lights belonged to one object. All of our neighbors came out to see it and everyone agreed it was different from anything we have ever witnessed.
Summary: 3 white lights in unison that moved across low in the sky. No blinking, no sound, moved slowing, appeared together as if one object. Nothing like an airplane or helicopter
